Package project4

Class RestStop

java.lang.Object
project4.RestStop
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<RestStop>
public class RestStop extends Object implements Comparable<RestStop>
Represents a single rest stop. This class stores the label of a rest stop along with a list of the supplies that a hiker can collect there and list of obstacles that a hiker may encounter.
